welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Chanhassen, a charming city known for its beautiful parks, theater productions, and friendly community. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer during your stay."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Flying Cloud Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal is exclusively for private flights and offers a more luxurious and personalized experience.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy complimentary WiFi throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal for domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The smaller terminal for low-cost carriers.

wifi.note: Limited free access, premium options available for purchase.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Crystal Airport serves all commercial flights and includes amenities such as restaurants, shops, and rental car counters.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Crystal Airport serves private and charter flights and includes a VIP lounge and concierge services.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Downtown Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Jet Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal caters to private jet owners and offers exclusive amenities and services.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Anoka County–Blaine Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers, including restaurants, shops, and rental car services.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Anoka County–Blaine Airport is equipped to handle a wide range of cargo and freight, providing efficient and reliable services for businesses and individuals.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
